===Plurality

    Plurality is marked through reduplication of the first syllable, with the
removal of the (if present) C3. For example:

*Zobuz --- wild animal
*Zozobuz --- wild animals
*Monizь --- man
*Momonizь --- men
*Pnir --- woman
*Pnipnir --- women

===Agent nouns

    Agent nouns are formed through reduplication of the last syllable, with the
removal of the C1 and (if present) C2. For example:

*Kukьon --- professional cooking
*Kukьonon --- chef
*Lesьapь --- professional driving
*Lesьapьapь --- driver
*Kьobьet --- romantic love
*Kьobьetet --- lover

